'From Squeak3.7gamma of ''17 July 2004'' [latest update: #5976] on 17 July 2004 at 11:09:12 am'!"Change Set:		HasHaloFix-nkDate:			12 June 2004Author:			Ned KonzDespite a number of Morphs calling #hasHalo, it didn't work right.This change set makes sure that #hasHalo:true is called when a Morph gets a halo."!!HaloMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'nk 6/12/2004 21:56'!setTarget: aMorph	"Private!! Set the target without adding handles."	target _ aMorph topRendererOrSelf.	innerTarget _ target renderedMorph.	innerTarget wantsDirectionHandles		ifTrue: [self showDirectionHandles: true addHandles: false].	target hasHalo: true.! !